,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T00:03:05.000Z","msg":"冬天要做好保暖啊<br />\n夜晚有冇關好窗啊？"},{"pid":"6fb0081224f9e86ca0990fb9c9534b33beaa6e40","tid":936343,"uid":196078,"like":66,"dislike":2,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T00:08:47.000Z","msg":"扔咗就扔咗啦,樓主唔好兜啦"},{"pid":"2504b060435111d0611b7388e5ba37a73705f992","tid":936343,"uid":6297,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T00:32:20.000Z","msg":"咪撚嚇樓豬啦<br />\n<br />\n十五度又室內動物邊覺得凍呀！得連登毒撚先至會講十五度要凍到冬眠"},{"pid":"2970c442ebf746894a3036c60911717331b8b567","tid":936343,"uid":121544,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T00:51:09.000Z","msg":"真係冬眠既話用風筒吹佢會醒返"},{"pid":"7859313e3f6689108790626b1550e9eb883dc458","tid":936343,"uid":280,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T01:09:33.000Z","msg":"殺鼠凶手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c56fa2b1bb5e90cc07d5159da691d00b9725ec","tid":936343,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T01:10:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c69a1fd8c91c72258a2e4e76ad8c7b1b35d3d85","tid":936343,"uid":271,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T01:17:14.000Z","msg":"第一 唔好俾任何棉花佢 佢地好易吸左影響呼吸<br />\n第二 唔好用風筒吹呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  啲鼠你直接吹風就唔病都變病 <br />\n<br />\n係唔係你喂錯糧俾佢呀 你平時俾咩佢食<br />\n仲有 用咩底材 同埋天氣凍 你要預啲底材要鋪滿成個籠同要有少少厚度 再加個木屋俾佢就最好 佢地會將啲底材搬哂俾屋架啦"},{"pid":"35584bea4d006f446b3dab1b4fba79fef0f5b192","tid":936343,"uid":45289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T01:22:31.000Z","msg":"係咪冬眠咋"},{"pid":"99b7c5742dd911c07dbbdacce23e884a10814661","tid":936343,"uid":25530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T01:24:20.000Z","msg":"唔好用綿花 用碎廚房紙<br />\n再買暖墊/保暖燈俾佢啦"},{"pid":"1bf57947afe5ac502e848a1323eb950d990901d1","tid":936343,"uid":25530,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"35584bea4d006f446b3dab1b4fba79fef0f5b192","tid":936343,"uid":45289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T01:22:31.000Z","msg":"係咪冬眠咋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T01:26:15.000Z","msg":"唔可以俾佢冬眠架"},{"pid":"a0fb1a1fcc4458d182044bc765a60986b448b7ab","tid":936343,"uid":49222,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"1bf57947afe5ac502e848a1323eb950d990901d1","tid":936343,"uid":25530,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"35584bea4d006f446b3dab1b4fba79fef0f5b192","tid":936343,"uid":45289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T01:22:31.000Z","msg":"係咪冬眠咋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T01:26:15.000Z","msg":"唔可以俾佢冬眠架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T01:32:12.000Z","msg":"最好唔好俾佢冬眠囉，無做足御寒真係冬眠左都無計，但起碼未死先<br />\n樓主果隻如果真係死左，唔好要買住，過左冬天先，唔想有多個受害者<br />\n利申: 3隻鼠，其中一隻熊仔"},{"pid":"54d31b442fbbabf2954711300fd9e631596a4ffd","tid":936343,"uid":20368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T02:08:03.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪死左<br />\n不如去獸醫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489526dcb7f1d8b57ff14be67cacde7c2b314208","tid":936343,"uid":186961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2504b060435111d0611b7388e5ba37a73705f992","tid":936343,"uid":6297,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T00:32:20.000Z","msg":"咪撚嚇樓豬啦<br />\n<br />\n十五度又室內動物邊覺得凍呀！得連登毒撚先至會講十五度要凍到冬眠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T02:13:15.000Z","msg":"家養細鼠，如果本身身體弱少少<br />\n呢啲天氣已經要冬眠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc646e251ef84baf25c1f26232a2fdcc6c9293d","tid":936343,"uid":22590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T02:14:56.000Z","msg":"我隻熊仔鼠呢邊-2度都未凍死(室內溫度計19度)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會有其他病?"},{"pid":"71145086d75d755bd97a34686ecb4273921ce811","tid":936343,"uid":59090,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T02:33:59.000Z","msg":"死左架啦 冬眠唔會無反應"},{"pid":"805b73b7247629d0d3f2ce771955780617ac22d0","tid":936343,"uid":107166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2504b060435111d0611b7388e5ba37a73705f992","tid":936343,"uid":6297,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T00:32:20.000Z","msg":"咪撚嚇樓豬啦<br />\n<br />\n十五度又室內動物邊覺得凍呀！得連登毒撚先至會講十五度要凍到冬眠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T02:52:16.000Z","msg":"咁倉鼠本身最適溫度係20幾度既 <br />\n可能棉花塞腸出事都唔定"},{"pid":"5cea5ff19fb94010faae452ad5f4494abf183980","tid":936343,"uid":2144,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T03:35:00.000Z","msg":"如果新手一開始養熊仔鼠要好小心，因為熊仔鼠相對其他鼠細膽，一開始盡量俾多啲時間佢適應，唔好咁急同佢玩住，加上呢排天氣凍，要多啲墊材保暖在所難免<br />\n見上面有巴打話會因為棉花而塞咗氣管，所以要多啲留意下佢，一開始唔好用太多棉花（我通常拎一細個拳頭嘅棉花）<br />\n我一開始都係養熊仔鼠，結果同樓主一樣大約一個禮拜隻倉鼠就因為傷風過身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n考慮自己能力之後養返肥肥鼠，依家養咗成半年多，仲肥咗好多（80g)，要幫佢減下肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以上係小弟小小心得，如果樓主想了解多啲可以去YouTube 打 卡爾，佢有好多養倉鼠資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望樓主隻熊仔鼠最後武士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6541ab462c32e29009c325c3b022667fc75232e2","tid":936343,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T03:35:43.000Z","msg":"用綿花會出事"},{"pid":"90a0e012e4bac1b57b43aa6e1dcc536905ebfc85","tid":936343,"uid":200578,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"6541ab462c32e29009c325c3b022667fc75232e2","tid":936343,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T03:35:43.000Z","msg":"用綿花會出事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T03:45:23.000Z","msg":"有啲綿花係比鼠鼠吸入都會溶返 唔會塞住咖~<br />\n我上年有比鼠鼠用 而家都冇事touch wood 仲好開心望住我拎瓜子食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2443684e4dae0c03e971416d92c47bc09a1a9d3","tid":936343,"uid":121744,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T03:54:05.000Z","msg":"你玩咩啊，拎條賓周拍佢塊面啊？<br />\n<br />\n肯定嚇死佢喇"},{"pid":"a3f01e7b4bd0b5d56cfa20dcd38cde83884696fb","tid":936343,"uid":3167,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T04:05:30.000Z","msg":"屌你老母未撚養啦弱智仔"},{"pid":"0f1c21612cc916abf6a8740af6a45a9050001792","tid":936343,"uid":36104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3fa059f50c6212054f641a15d1792f66a2494784","tid":936343,"uid":123702,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"quote":{"pid":"e243654fc7a29ba29eebe6573624da975a3fd673","tid":936343,"uid":191765,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T20:19:00.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪驚佢原來真係冬眠但已經扔咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依加唔敢應group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T23:30:57.000Z","msg":"試過用風筒吹 都完全冇反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點解咁突然<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T04:11:21.000Z","msg":"試下瞓瞓下覺<br />\n搵人一盆滾水潑鳩你<br />\n有冇腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3315a4977502ac0075604159baffd8b37870c98","tid":936343,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T04:14:01.000Z","msg":"鼠會冬眠架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3c24b0a177a4beec3d7e95b769ac10916b4efa","tid":936343,"uid":36104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0fb1a1fcc4458d182044bc765a60986b448b7ab","tid":936343,"uid":49222,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"1bf57947afe5ac502e848a1