/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實係重咗1g左右<br />\n至於我話肥係因為之前聽過醫生講70-80g對肥肥鼠黎講係叫肥，但見佢跑得食得我諗冇咩問題，不過都要控制下佢啲食量（好鐘意收埋野食）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T06:42:52.000Z","msg":"80g唔重啊嘛？<br />\n我之前隻熊仔鼠（女）帶去睇獸醫，85g左右<br />\n獸醫話佢偏輕，我仲講隻野食好多野，獸醫開嘅藥水佢好鐘意食<br />\n獸醫話咁開多啲，等我隻鼠可以上番正常體重<br />\n<br />\n我而家隻仔，成140g<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我仲嫌佢唔夠肥"},{"pid":"7830e3e0f2b5f7e8315b64c3cbfac18f95630fd2","tid":936343,"uid":49222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa4290f553e5d89539cff2237ef4bf6d1b1bb60d","tid":936343,"uid":143805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T06:32:22.000Z","msg":"想問下除左比多啲廚紙之外仲有咩方法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽過有電暖墊又或者保暖燈 但邊到有得買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T06:51:05.000Z","msg":"去商場廁所拎抹手紙都得既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淘寶，不過宜家都已經凍，你趕唔切送，等其他巴打答"},{"pid":"9b075c8150d542c29f227d38ad0ac1c1b8c28aab","tid":936343,"uid":186961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7830e3e0f2b5f7e8315b64c3cbfac18f95630fd2","tid":936343,"uid":49222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa4290f553e5d89539cff2237ef4bf6d1b1bb60d","tid":936343,"uid":143805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T06:32:22.000Z","msg":"想問下除左比多啲廚紙之外仲有咩方法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽過有電暖墊又或者保暖燈 但邊到有得買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T06:51:05.000Z","msg":"去商場廁所拎抹手紙都得既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淘寶，不過宜家都已經凍，你趕唔切送，等其他巴打答"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-